pageContext.claim: “@OANN is doing incredible reporting. If Lamestream Media did the same, they would get respect back. At All-Time Low! [linking to a segment promoting a conspiracy theory about Ukraine and the 2016 U.S. election].”
pageContext.analysis: In this tweet, the president directs his followers to a segment promoting a debunked conspiracy theory that Ukraine and not Russia interfered in the 2016 U.S. election.
